\item `120`
\end{itemize}

When we call `factorial(5)`, it returns `120` because `120` is the result of multiplying `5` by `factorial(4)`. When we call `factorial(4)`, it returns `24` because `24` is the result of multiplying `4` by `factorial(3)`. And so on.

